CBRE is pleased to offer Lot 1/1475-1477 Sydney Road, Campbellfield, for sale.

+ Dual street access 
+ Full drive-through capability

+ Available Now! 

Please contact the marketing agents to arrange an inspection or for further information.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Killen & Thomas are pleased to introduce 1537-1549 Sydney Road, Campbellfield to the market for sale via Public Auction on Thursday 18th May 2017 at 12:00pm on-site.

The property is situated on Sydney Road within the industrial area of Campbellfield, a well-established northern suburb, 20kms* north of Melbourne's CBD.

Access to the site is excellent, being located only moments from the Hume Highway, Metropolitan Ring Road, Cooper Street and within close proximity to the Wholesale Fruit & Vegetable Market and Melbourne Airport.

The property offers immense diversity to potential purchasers with options for owner occupation, land banking and various development opportunities (STCA).

Key property attributes include:

- Significant corner site area: 17,392sqm*
- Industrial 1 Zone (IN1Z)
- 120 metre* frontage to Sydney Road and 160 metre* frontage to Decco Drive
- Highly diverse development potential (STCA)
- Exposure to a high volume of passing traffic to both local and interstate commuters

For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection of the site, kindly contact the exclusively listed agents.

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to offer 25 & 35 Berwick Road, Campbellfield for sale via Expressions of Interest closing Wednesday 5th December at 3.00pm (AEDT).

This strategically located industrial development opportunity is situated 18km* north of the Melbourne CBD within the heart of the northern industrial precinct of Campbellfield.

The properties are well accessed by a number of key transport arterials including Sydney Road/Hume Highway, Metropolitan Ring Road, Hume Freeway, Camp Road and Cooper Street.

Key property attributes include:

- Combined site area: 16,122sqm* 
- 25 Berwick Road site area: 9,915sqm*
- 35 Berwick Road site area: 6,197sqm* 
- Combined frontage to Berwick Road of 100* metres 
- Industrial 1 Zone (IN1Z) 
 
For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection of the property, kindly contact the marketing representatives at CBRE.

*approx.
